        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for copy of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p>  
<p>Discusses Pangenesis and considers CD’s "gemmules" comparable to his own hypothetical "physiological units" ["On alleged ""spontaneous generation"", and on the hypothesis of physiological units", appendix in <hi rend="italic">The principles of biology</hi>, vol. 1 (1864)].</p> 
